District B13;;78;;80;;R;;In 21st-century Paris, a member (Cyril Raffaelli) of an elite police squad must enter a crime-ridden ghetto to defuse a bomb that has fallen into the hands of Taha (Larbi Naceri), a powerful hoodlum. The cop joins forces with a civilian (David Belle) who must rescue his sister (Dany Verissimo) from the same criminal who holds the bomb.;;Action,Mystery & thriller,Sci-fi;;Pierre Morel;;2006;;Cyril Raffaelli,David Belle,Tony D'Amario,Bibi Naceri,Dany Verissimo,François Chattot,Nicolas Woirion,Patrick Olivier,Samir Guesmi,Jérôme Gadner;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/district_b13